Author: mskmcclure
Text: I like it and feel like I’m getting a little bit more every time I read or listen to a podcast. I know the only way to stop the urges is to dismiss them. I have not mastered this yet but I am determined. I know if it weren’t for the urges I’d see no point to n stuffing my face with tons of junk. Like right now I’ll be had a good day. I’m calm. It’s just knowing how to and successfully dismissing the urge to binge in order to make them stop. I pray pray I get this soon. B.E.D had ruined my life
